clone(address,uint16,string,string,uint8.details: called by the delivery contract to clone a non existing Htoken in this chain, of a native token in forgein chain

params.decimals: decimals of Htoken(same as native token) in src chain
params.name: name of Htoken in src chain
params.nativeChainId: the native chainId of the token to be cloned
params.nativeToken: the native token to be cloned
params.symbol: symbol of Htoken in src chain

returns._0: the address of the cloned token. Htoken.

unwrap(address,uint256,address).details: unwrap a Htoke to get the native token.called will get the same amount of Native token.

params.amount: the amount of Htoken to unwrapped
params.to: the receipient address of native token
params.token: the Htoken to be unwrapped to

wrap(address,uint256,address).details: wrap only a native token in the local chain, holds the native token and mint to the user Htokens

params.amount: the amount of native token to be wrapped .
params.token: the native token to be wrapped

unwrap(address,uint256,address).notice: only can unwrap a token in it's native chain.

wrap(address,uint256,address).notice: rebasing tokens and token with fee on transfer may cause lose of funds it should be only one Htoken for each native token.
